project_descr: This project is  a low-cost, high impact initiative; a multi-track agenda in which innovative new development technologies and methodologies are fully utilised in order to position the citizen at the heart of development and government decision-making

outputs.output_descr: “Inno4Dev” is a joint initiative of EU and UNDP’s. The project will be executed through idea incubation for citizens and public servants, customized public awareness actions and public sector engagement.
